title: Yakshini
overview: From the twisted mind of writer Kasim Ansari comes a tale of supernatural terror. The new horror audio film "Yakshini" follows a young man who becomes enthralled by a beautiful woman, only to discover she is a witch who stalks the night. Will he escape her seductive clutches or face the chilling consequences? Listen to the bone-chilling audio film exclusively on the official app of Audio Pitara.
